Description. Body (
Fig. 27
) dark brownish, head blackish, anterior margin of pronotum, humeral spot, posterior margin of elytra, posterior margins of tergites, legs, palpi and first two antennomeres brownish-yellow. Pronotum, elytra, and abdomen with distinct bluish hue.

Distribution. Widely distributed from Western Yunnan and Sichuan to Taiwan (
Fig. 19
).
